name: Insect Invasion (Abualrahi Games)
description:
Game description:

You have to find the right key for the portal to move to a place where there is victory, but you will face insects that try to prevent you from getting the keys.

Control:

(W,A,S,D) Keys to moving.

(1,2) Keys to change gun.

Esc key to stop.

mouse to rotation
